document.title: Urban Assembly Maker Academy Content Standards 2015-16

25D311C2D4E842CF851E7FBE68CBECC7.description: Playmaking Techniques: I can demonstrate playmaking techniques throughout my design process, leading to the final realization of my work

932F2616EA9B46998D3DE06CA05297F4.description: Use Evidence: I can support my ideas with clearly documented and thoroughly explained evidence

D597AB59D7854F628B0CDA40DA7ADFC8.description: Theatrical Skills: I can demonstrate and explain my use of performance and expressive skills in my work

07C8DE6182F24B238DBB4B01CA2E9E73.description: Engage Content Knowledge: I can create explicit and thoughtful connections using my subject-specific knowledge such as dramatic elements

B76C6042705046E5B3A9224BEA070EA8.description: Kind and Productive: I can behave toward others in the community with kindness and respect, while remaining professional and focused on my task

91232411E9604AE6A9CFCB8718B33217.description: Meet Design Constraints: I can entirely meet all design constraints for my task
